{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaskade is a minimalist strategy game about connecting an evolving delivery network. It's about getting into a state of flow and painting a picture with a minimal toolset.\u00a0\u00a0 <br><br>Play the first two chapters of Kaskade in the Demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/Buidl_Sequence_Final_w_Border.gif?t=1738939143\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the Demo you can unlock the core abilities from the main game, make permanent upgrades between runs, and compare your high score on the leaderboard.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/Alt_Widgets_640x360_wBorder.gif?t=1738939143\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Connect inputs to outputs that match in color to earn credits. Spend credits to unlock new abilities. Use those new abilities to make managing your network more effective. Rinse and repeat.\u00a0<br><br>Permadeath!\u00a0Too many false moves and it will be game over! There is no save system, but there is a roguelite progression between runs.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/Deconstructed_wBorder.gif?t=1738939143\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the first two Chapters from the main game on normal and hard difficulty.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A zen, puzzle experience or a strategic, roguelite challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key abilities to unlock (Jump, Double Jump, Switch, and Pause)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boons and upgrades to purchase to manage more and more deliveries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Colorblind mode (deliveries have clear labels)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mouse and keyboard support (gamepads are not recommended)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738939143","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/page.bg.jpg?t=1738939143","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/33880fb8f7553c3de8fb2c7c6a15f6245ac1fd1d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738939143","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/33880fb8f7553c3de8fb2c7c6a15f6245ac1fd1d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738939143","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaskade is a minimalist strategy game about connecting an evolving delivery network. It's about getting into a state of flow and painting a picture with a minimal toolset.\u00a0\u00a0 <br><br>Play the first two chapters of Kaskade in the Demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/Buidl_Sequence_Final_w_Border.gif?t=1738939143\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the Demo you can unlock the core abilities from the main game, make permanent upgrades between runs, and compare your high score on the leaderboard.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/Alt_Widgets_640x360_wBorder.gif?t=1738939143\" /></p><p cl